WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.880
Three strikers, three defenses that can't handle them. This card should be free.

00:05.660 --> 00:09.900
We're starting with Ronaldo over one and a half shots on target. He's averaging almost

00:09.900 --> 00:15.920
two a game over his last ten international starts and DR Congo foul for fun, which hands him the

00:15.920 --> 00:21.440
set pieces and penalties to test that keeper all night. Fernandez and Leão are going to feed him

00:21.440 --> 00:27.800
in the box non-stop, then water him in over a half a shot on target. He's Panama's main threat,

00:27.800 --> 00:33.320
clearing this lately, and Croatia plays that high line and bleeds four and a half on target

00:33.320 --> 00:39.360
a game. He only needs one counter to catch this, and we're capping it with Harry Kane anytime

00:39.360 --> 00:45.740
score, seven of his last ten, and Ghana just shipped twelve on target with a backline in chaos.

00:46.560 --> 00:51.520
He's on penalties and every set piece, so we're going to roll with that three leg parlay.

00:51.520 --> 00:53.120
This one's almost guaranteed.

